name: SILLY SKELLY
description:
Halloween Edition

I left that silly old me years ago, when I wandered through souls in search of joy. I left her, but somehow it's still at the back of my head sometimes. Just sitting there doing nothing. Watching me like I'm some sort of a parade. But as she was looking at me, I looked back at her with light in my heart telling her that you are one hell of a silly thing, but it's okay because you were once mine. 

Brushed with Photoshop by spicyaries
